sentences: Ä°lker Kaan Kaleli (born 11 May 1984) is a Turkish actor best known for his role in Poyraz Karayel.
In 2014, he appeared in the film Silsile.
From 2015 to 2017, Kaleli played the leading character in Poyraz Karayel, for which he received a Golden Butterfly Award as best actor in 2016.
